### Create user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "me@local",
  "name": "Me",
  "password": "changeme",
  "isActive": true
}

### Get user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1

### Create account
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "name": "Main",
  "broker": "IBKR",
  "baseCurrency": "USD",
  "timezone": "America/Toronto",
  "isActive": true
}

### List accounts by user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/by-user/1
